special envoy of Libyan leader Muammar Qaddafi, in a meeting today
that China appreciates the flexible, practical and wise attitude
of the Libyan government in handling the Lockerbie problem and
praised Libya's contribution to calming regional conflicts and
strengthening unity on the African continent.
</P>
