<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Closes Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, August 23 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at
Tehran Stock Exchange closed at 1730.55 points Monday, up 10.47
points from Sunday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 1,553,632 shares changed hands in 905 deals, and the
turnover was 10.5 billion rials (about 3.5 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
Shares of 46 companies made gains, and those of 19 others
declined. 
