<HEADLINE> ECOWAS to Hold Meeting on Liberian Conflict </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ABUJA, August 23 (Xinhua) -- Seven foreign ministers of the
Economic Community of West African States (ECOWAS) would hold a
one-day meeting in Lome, Togo's capital, Thursday to discuss the
insurgency in northern Liberia.
</P>
