<HEADLINE> Highlight of Diplomatic News Today (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
State Councilor Wu Yi, in a meeting today with Singaporean
Minister for Trade and Industry George Yeo, said that Singaporean
businessmen are welcome to invest in China's high-tech sector and
central and western parts of the country.
