countries and will lay a good foundation for further friendly
cooperation by the two armed forces.
</P>
<P>
Papua New Guinea Adheres to One China Policy
</P>
<P>
The Papua New Guinean government adheres to the one China
policy, and recognizes that Taiwan is an inalienable part of the
Chinese territory, and it does not develop official ties with
Taiwan.
</P>
<P>
