<BODY>
<HEADLINE> World Athletics Championships Results (6) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
200 meters first round (top three in each heat plus two fastest
losers to quarter-finals):
</P>
<P>
Heat 1:
</P>
<P>
1. Francis Obikwelu, Nigeria, 20.54 seconds
</P>
<P>
2. Glenn Smith, Canada, 20.68
</P>
<P>
3. Joseph Batangdon, Cameroon, 20.76
</P>
<P>
4. Panogiotis Sarris, Greece, 20.78
</P>
<P>
5. Sergey Slkukin, Russia, 20.92
</P>
<P>
6. Kim Collins, St Kitts, 20.95
